Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:38.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have lived for all these years… without ever making a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:42.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,This… is my penance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was unable to become \Nan Eternal Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nor was I able to go \Nto another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I remained here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to touch another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:58.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to be held by another. Yet still…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:01:59.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:03.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why? Why did your body\N have to become like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I refused to choose a sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:11.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was chosen to become \Nthe keeper of the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you wouldn’t choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:17.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that future maidens would not err the way I have erred.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,To continue to stand here…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is my punishment for continuing to run from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:45.47,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Choices
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:50.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is to be\N formally disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, we have decided that you must now go to the Spring.
Comment: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:58.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why must we also give up\N our standing as sibyllae?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:02.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of your duties will be taken over by priestesses from the Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re not even allowed to be Simoun sibyllae anymore? So that means…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can’t stay here\N on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well… forcing them to make such a choice all of a sudden…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:23.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can they be expected \Nto decide so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,They need to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are asking only for a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:32.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Compared to the long history of the Simulacrum Theocracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,it is but a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:45.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,You heard about what \Nhappened to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:51.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m going to be leaving\N the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:01.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Holy Land has no desire to fly the Simoun any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:04.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,To demonstrate the fact, our entire maintenance crew is being relocated to the Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wherever we end up, \Nit’s all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:12.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun are the holy \Nchariots of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:13.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard\N I try to get close…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. The truth is that\N I’ve realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t care about \Nthe Simoun any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll be happy as long as you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can understand if you despise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’ve gotten smaller, haven’t they?
Comment: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:41.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:51.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become a man and tinker with the Simoun with you, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you going to choose?
Comment: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:15.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:19.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess you always\N wanted to be a man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:22.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bet you don’t even care that\N they’re forcing us to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you’re always—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not true!
Comment: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:28.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m scared too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s scary becoming an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want someone to help me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to be protected! But even so…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forget it, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re such a dummy, Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:52.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy… dummy…\N dummy… dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fighting with your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, you guys are so childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:06.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re still kids. It’s too early \Nfor you to become adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:12.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Vyura, everyone in Rubor already chose their sex, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ones who were going to inherit a family business became men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest… well, you know, it depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about you, Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:24.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me? Whatever. I don’t really\N care which sex I end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:27.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I’m sure I wouldn’t be saying that if I had a lover, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:31.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? But everyone told me \Nthat you liked Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I keep telling \Nthem that’s not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it doesn’t really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,But… I dunno…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It feels kinda lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s what… becoming an adult is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see… so becoming an adult is a lonely thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti’s an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez, that’s why I told you not to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re always such a drag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re a dummy, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:16.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who’re you calling a dummy? Dodo-legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine! Go back on your own then, loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Du-Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Du… mmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re a dummy, Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even when we quarrelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:43.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,she couldn’t even think\N of words to insult me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,So all she ever said was “dummy.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:52.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you know, she just never gave up, and kept tagging along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:55.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seriously… what a dummy\N I have for a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:08:00.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder when Alti…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,…stopped being such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’ll be the one to protect you, Nee-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,She got this determined look in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:14.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Her arms and legs grew longer, and it was almost like… she became more of an adult than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:19.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lots of things were happening\N all the time, so I didn’t even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That Alti…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,…she’s still the same old idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I kept looking the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn’t want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,But… even so, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’ll forgive you.
Comment: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:35.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are things that you can still do,\Neven if you’re no longer a sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such as forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,To forgive a fault…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and to be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:49.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think we can still be sibyllae even after we choose our sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really {\i1}do{\i0} like you, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:09:00.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,My feelings won’t change whether I become a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I’ll never stop respecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:17.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve heard that the High Priestess has left the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, we don’t have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to say?
Comment: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:24.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, don’t bother answering. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I can tell you this.\N There’s no way I’ll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:36.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Going to another world just ’cause you wanna see Amuria again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:39.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s all you care about!\N So I can’t do a Ri Maajon with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:47.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did Onashia show me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:52.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never to be held by another. Yet still…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:55.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remain here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:10:00.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia… will she have to\N stand there forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to be forgiven by anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:08.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:13.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought that perhaps I should take some of Mamiina’s belongings with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:16.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh. Her suitcase is under her bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:23.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,When I return home,\N Mamiina’s mother will be there, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that I could\N give these to her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,It still smells like Mamiina…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:35.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope this will comfort \Nher mother, even if only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:40.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we even… \Nsave anyone anymore?
Comment: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:47.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think it will be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:50.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,We struggle so much\N just to save ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,But… perhaps if we try\N really, really hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,…maybe we can save \Nat least one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,One… person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, do you have somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,That one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun… disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:12.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard that the Highland soldiers are looking for her, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun… why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe she didn’t wanna \Nbecome an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. Yun, she…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,She must have found…
Comment: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whatever. She’s so standoffish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just leaving like that, \Nwithout even saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:34.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah… but once Chor Tempest is disbanded, we’re all gonna go our separate ways anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:42.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is something that \NI need to tell you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,About another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:11.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s crazy! To think \Nthe Emerald Ri Maajon did that…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it will save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soon, we will all choose our sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our lives here on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} \Nwill come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:30.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,But those two… they won’t choose a sex, and they’ll stay the way they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not choose their sex…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and stay the way they are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,When we all become adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:42.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,and the feelings that \Nwe have now fade away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:46.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,in some other time, those two…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:51.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,will stand in the shining lands, looking just as they do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So those two will…{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:58.78,0:12:59.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if we all become adults…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}…they’ll remain as they are now, forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The eternal now…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:14.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you don’t want to, you don’t have to go to the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what we decide,\N we should at least tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,That we’ve not going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t need to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to know what \Nhappened to Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one I love…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,…is you.
Comment: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:44.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:51.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love you, who strive \Nfor life in spite of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:56.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love you, who saved me \Nfrom the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:59.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m scared of going to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:02.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if I’m with you, I think—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:09.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn’t want… to hear your feelings… about liking me and stuff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t need to give me an answer.
Comment: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:11.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:15.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just thought that I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:18.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was so sudden! I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one I love… is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:56.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:37.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to save the wandering \Nspirits of my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was the thought \Nthat kept me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,But… I always knew the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,That the dead can\N no longer be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:57.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. I realized that there’s \None soul that only I can save.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had secretly hoped…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,…that you would say \Nthose words to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Long ago, I decided \Nnot to choose a sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:22.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, my heart was unable \Nto stay a maiden’s heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:26.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now… I am trying to \Nrun away, once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,while pushing all my\N responsibilities onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:31.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are… beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,It sounds very lively out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That voice… that has to be Sibylla Floe.
Comment: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uwaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, were you ever \Nplanning to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:09.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s our last day on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:12.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait! Alti!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nah, don’t think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:15.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:25.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,The view is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,C’mon, let’s dance, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, let the {\i1}Messis{\i0}\N carry you to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nah, it’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:35.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve always wanted to ride \Non a helical motor train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:42.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,May I ask what has happened to Sibylla Neviril and Sibylla Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:45.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,They said that they wished \Nfor a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:50.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,After I’m an adult, \NI’ll come visit again!
Comment: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,The mountains are getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,It should be lunchtime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:43.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh! I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:47.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I asked for some snacks before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is anyone hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those look yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want the veggie one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:55.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Rodore?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll have meat, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me, too, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Boy, am I hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mmm, delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:06.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is Rodore’s, and here you go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:07.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Man, if you had sandwiches, you should’ve told us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:24.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:26.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
