Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:09.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,And so, the girls head\N towards adulthood,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:12.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,and Neviril and Aaeru \Ntowards their “eternal now.”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:15.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:17.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pair.
